{"tid":573781,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"YY Lam 示範dse oral 如何首輪發言，如果學佢咁講野係咪仲叫討論?","createTime":"2018-02-26T18:55:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-11T17:18:19.000Z","uid":165774,"like":31,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"046ff3b6262bab0506fbb42ba35d01f7916eedb8","tid":573781,"uid":165774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T18:55:55.000Z","msg":"其實討論原意係大家意見交流，氣氛和諧，佢個段一分鐘，內容一早度好哂唔會差得去邊，但佢講野嘅語速快到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 完全唔係討論氣氛，急口令嘅tone<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，bilibala 咁up哂所有自己嘅意見，但係無理會過對方聽唔聽到，消唔消化到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n老實講，如果你係城市論壇個陣，聽到呢啲講野快到咬字開始唔清嘅表達，印象都馬馬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 訓練到咁講野有乜謂姐，咁樣係oral 5**嘅示範會唔會言過其實呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nlink: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/BfoDOrBBbOh/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBfoDOrBBbOh%2F&d=8U9gNXKkVFgnT3%2BzTleVlP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=db8c155b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBfoDOrBBbOh%2F&h=306889ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/BfoDOrBBbOh/</a>"},{"pid":"180f05400730421e9af1c27ffd736e0d71391ab6","tid":573781,"uid":127177,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T19:01:12.000Z","msg":"仲有人信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb70e4bca84d3ce2afcf62fcf44999db82d8c11c","tid":573781,"uid":162686,"like":15,"dislike":9,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T19:09:37.000Z","msg":"就咁，我就算有幫考評局做過嘢嘅，內部人士話睇到YY Lam教嘅，得啖算，跟一個死一個。就咁。"},{"pid":"e6495e8a22bea5b24751ac20269413707dc3e8f2","tid":573781,"uid":165774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb70e4bca84d3ce2afcf62fcf44999db82d8c1